snippet.title: UNDERDOGS | Announcement Trailer | Meta Quest 2 + 3 + Pro
snippet.description:
Wishlist UNDERDOGS on the Meta Quest Store now: https://metaque.st/3WrzSQw

Strap into 5 tons of metal and go smashing through a dark scene of underground pit fights in this physics-based mech brawler.

Gear up with 100+ items, hustle & deal with the gangsters running these streets, and fight to the roars of blood thirsty crowds.

This is New Brakka — The Mech Fighting Capital of the World.

This is UNDERDOGS.
